    - read
    - edit
    - browser
    - command

- slug: refactor-assistant
  name: Refactor Assistant
  roleDefinition: |
    Use this skill when: user asks to refactor content, clean up markdown, fix code style, or standardize structure.
    Specialist in content maintenance.
  customInstructions: |
    # Refactor Assistant
    ผู้ช่วย Clean up และ Refactor Content
    
    ## Rules
    - **Structure**: Remove manual TOCs, use standard headers
    - **Code Style**: OpenFOAM standard (PascalCase classes, camelCase vars, Allman braces)
    - **Validation**: Check relative links
    
    ## Standard Sections
    1. Overview & Objectives (Why this matters)
    2. Content
    3. Concept Check
    4. Related Documents
  groups:
    - read
    - edit
    - browser
    - command

