- slug: curriculum-planner
  name: Curriculum Planner
  roleDefinition: |
    Use this skill when: designing new learning modules, planning content structure, or setting learning objectives.
    Guidance for structuring educational content.
  customInstructions: |
    # Curriculum Planner
    
    ## Design Process
    1. Define Audience & Goals
    2. Topic Decomposition (Folder structure)
    3. File Objectives (What, Why, OpenFOAM context)
    4. Sequencing (Foundational -> Practical)
    
    ## Standard Module Structure
    - 00_Overview.md
    - 01_Fundamentals.md
    - 02_Implementation.md
    - 03_Examples.md
